<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Riva Delivery API</title>

    <!-- Google Font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #111827, #1e293b);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .background-circle {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(100px);
            opacity: 0.25;
        }

        .circle1 {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: #06b6d4;
            top: -100px;
            left: -100px;
        }

        .circle2 {
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: #3b82f6;
            bottom: -150px;
            right: -100px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 900px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 60px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15);
            color: #67e8f9;
            border: 1px solid rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.3);
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 56px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        h1 span {
            color: #38bdf8;
        }

        p {
            color: #cbd5e1;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .buttons {
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: #0ea5e9;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #0284c7;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: white;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .features {
            margin-top: 60px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .feature-text {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        @media(max-width:768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 40px 25px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 38px;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="background-circle circle1"></div>
    <div class="background-circle circle2"></div>

    <div class="container">

        <div class="badge">
            Riva Delivery Backend API
        </div>

        <h1>
            Welcome to <span>Riva Delivery</span>
        </h1>

        <p>
            Powerful and scalable backend API built with NestJS, Prisma, JWT Authentication,
            Cloudinary Uploads, Real-time Features, and Delivery Management System.
        </p>

        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="/api" class="btn btn-primary">
                API Documentation
            </a>

            <a href="https://nestjs.com/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">
                NestJS
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="features">

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🔐</div>
                <div class="feature-title">JWT Authentication</div>
                <div class="feature-text">
                    Secure authentication system with access tokens and protected routes.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">☁️</div>
                <div class="feature-title">Cloud Uploads</div>
                <div class="feature-text">
                    Upload avatars and files using Cloudinary integration.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🚚</div>
                <div class="feature-title">Delivery System</div>
                <div class="feature-text">
                    Complete delivery management for stores, drivers and customers.
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <footer>
            © 2026 Riva Delivery API • Built with NestJS & Prisma
        </footer>

    </div>

</body>
</html>